Package: rmilter
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libmilter1.0.1, libopendkim6, libspf2-2, libpcre3
Description: Rmilter is sendmail milter for different checks of mail
 Rmilter provides the following features:
 .
 * SPF checks;
 .
 * greylisting using memcached storage;
 .
 * ratelimits using memcached storage;
 .
 * checking mail via rspamd/spamassassin;
 .
 * checking mail via clamav antivirus;
 .
 * regexp filters;
 .
 * DKIM signing;
 .
 * beanstalk operations for specific messages.
 .
 Rmilter uses sendmail milter interface and is compatible with Sendmail and Postfix MTA 
 as well as with other MTA that supports milter interface.
